  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK477">
<l>āṟṟi ṉaḷavaṟin tīka vatuporuḷ</l>
<l> pōṟṟi vaḻaṅku neṟi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let a man know the measure of his ability (to give), and let him give accordingly; such giving is the way to preserve his property.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
